<guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/russias-defence-minister-visits-north-korea-agencies-report-2024-11-29/</guid></item><item><title>西尼亚表示，芬兰-德国海底电缆在破裂后已恢复</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/finland-germany-undersea-cable-restored-after-breach-cinia-says-2024-11-29/</link><description>芬兰 Cinia 公司周五表示，该公司已完全修复 11 月 18 日断裂的 C-Lion1 海底光缆。</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 07:29:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/finland-germany-undersea-cable-restored-after-breach-cinia-says-2024-11-29/</guid></item><item><title>两极分化使议程复杂化，南非掌舵 G20</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/africa/south-africa-takes-g20-helm-polarisation-complicates-agenda-2024-11-29/</link><description>南非周日接任 G20 主席国，成为第一个主持该论坛的非洲国家，尽管其对包容性增长和气候变化等问题的关注可能会与贸易战和外交紧张的严峻现实相抵触。</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 07:11:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/africa/south-africa-takes-g20-helm-polarisation-complicates-agenda-2024-11-29/</guid></item><item><title>据第一财经报道，中国电动汽车制造商比亚迪向数十家供应商要求降价</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-ev-maker-byd-asks-dozens-suppliers-price-cuts-yicai-reports-2024-11-29/</link><description>国有新闻媒体第一财经周五援引未透露姓名的消息来源报道称，中国电动汽车制造商比亚迪已要求数十家供应商降价。</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 06:54:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-ev-maker-byd-asks-dozens-suppliers-price-cuts-yicai-reports-2024-11-29/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，物流供应商普洛斯正考虑于 2025 年在香港上市</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/logistics-provider-glp-is-considering-hong-kong-listing-2025-sources-say-2024-11-29/</link><description>三位直接了解此事的消息人士称，物流公司普洛斯正在考虑最早可能于明年在香港上市，八年前，这家在新加坡注册成立的公司被一个投资者集团私有化。</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 06:47:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/logistics-provider-glp-is-considering-hong-kong-listing-2025-sources-say-2024-11-29/</guid></item><item><title>首席执行官新疆言论被报道后，优衣库面临在中国遭到抵制的风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/uniqlo-risks-boycott-china-after-ceos-xinjiang-comment-2024-11-29/</link><description>休闲装巨头优衣库在中国面临着消费者抵制的呼声，此前英国广播公司(BBC)报道援引其所有者首席执行官的话说，该公司不从中国新疆地区采购棉花，该地区近年来面临强迫劳动的指控。</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 06:37:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/uniqlo-risks-boycott-china-after-ceos-xinjiang-comment-2024-11-29/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲黄金 印度黄金溢价稳定，价格波动稳定需求</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/asia-gold-india-gold-premiums-steady-price-fluctuations-stabilise-demand-2024-11-29/</link><description>印度的实物黄金溢价保持稳定，因为本周价格调整带来的需求上升随后被利率上升所抵消，而亚洲其他主要中心和最大消费国中国的需求仍然低迷。</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 06:13:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/asia-gold-india-gold-premiums-steady-price-fluctuations-stabilise-demand-2024-11-29/</guid></item><item><title>首尔称中国和俄罗斯军机进入韩国防空区</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/chinese-russian-military-planes-enter-south-koreas-air-defence-zone-seoul-says-2024-11-29/</link><description>韩国军方表示，周五，11架中国和俄罗斯军机在四个小时内进入韩国防空识别区，促使韩国出动战斗机。</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 05:54:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/chinese-russian-military-planes-enter-south-koreas-air-defence-zone-seoul-says-2024-11-29/</guid></item><item><title>早盘买盘：东京通胀数据公布后，日元多头继续前进</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-11-29/</link><description>Stella Qiu 展望欧洲和全球市场未来一天</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 05:32:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-11-29/</guid></item><item><title>独家：汇丰银行在艰难扩张后退出中国信用卡业务</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hsbc-pulling-back-china-credit-card-business-after-struggling-expand-sources-say-2024-11-29/</link><description>知情人士称，汇丰银行在中国推出信用卡业务八年后，将撤出其在中国的信用卡业务，原因是该银行难以在全球第二大经济体扩张业务并实现盈利。</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 05:22:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hsbc-pulling-back-china-credit-card-business-after-struggling-expand-sources-say-2024-11-29/</guid></item><item><title>中国恢复深圳旅客赴香港多次签证</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-resumes-multiple-entry-visas-shenzhen-travellers-hong-kong-2024-11-29/</link><description>据新华社周五报道，中国放宽了深圳居民赴港签证限制，自 12 月 1 日起每年允许多次入境香港。</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 05:04:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-resumes-multiple-entry-visas-shenzhen-travellers-hong-kong-2024-11-29/</guid></item><item><title>分析师表示，华为认为 Mate 70 手机的吸引力正在减弱</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/huawei-sees-excitement-mate-70-phone-wane-analysts-say-2024-11-29/</link><description>券商 Jefferies 表示，华为新推出的 Mate 70 智能手机在中国的消费者热情有所下降，这可能会影响这家中国科技巨头今年的整体出货量，从而使苹果和其他中国品牌受益。</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 04:49:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/huawei-sees-excitement-mate-70-phone-wane-analysts-say-2024-11-29/</guid></item></channel></rss>